node.text:
Dang it! The last couple weekends have been rough. I got sick last Saturday and was sick through out the whole week. I had so much weakness in my body and was not feeling hot at all this Saturday which shows in my riding and my results. Unfortunately I just had to make my way through the motos. I haven’t been ill in a looong time like that so it’s bound to happen at some point. Frustrating but it is what it is. Couldn’t have waited another week……. 😩

📸 @trevornelsonofficial
